It seems there is a misunderstanding, as I have not received any specific execution results or code snippets from you to analyze. If you could provide the actual code or execution results from your interaction with the Factorio REPL Environment, I would be happy to review it and provide a detailed report on what you attempted to achieve, any errors that occurred, and the outcomes of your actions.

### Please provide:
1. The code or commands you executed.
2. Any error messages or unexpected outputs you encountered.
3. A brief description of what you were trying to accomplish.

Once I have that information, I can give you a comprehensive analysis and useful tips based on your experience. Thank you!
